# Documentation Practice

- Keep concise, high-signal docs in `docs/` per module (water, nitrogen, phenology, canopy, architecture).
- Update MkDocs navigation when adding docs; prefer equations/links where helpful.
- Use RAG on markdown when cross-referencing; reference local files with `[file](mdc:file)`.

Key files: [mkdocs.yml](mdc:mkdocs.yml), [docs/](mdc:docs/index.md)
